{"tid":33954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日太空船搭載拖網　用電磁吸宇宙垃圾","createTime":"2016-12-11T07:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T15:17:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"467993aa0f995fcd7d7f5308ba5f7e3322242943","tid":33954,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:26:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161210/1009303/%E3%80%90%E6%89%93%E6%8E%83%E5%9B%89%E3%80%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E8%88%B9%E6%90%AD%E8%BC%89%E6%8B%96%E7%B6%B2%E3%80%80%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB%E7%A3%81%E5%90%B8%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161210%2F1009303%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%258E%2583%25E5%259B%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E8%2588%25B9%25E6%2590%25AD%25E8%25BC%2589%25E6%258B%2596%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25A3%2581%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%25AE%2587%25E5%25AE%2599%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE&d=VFChOwYL9hlg7MsFh4RdmAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=4fc613b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161210/1009303/%E3%80%90%E6%89%93%E6%8E%83%E5%9B%89%E3%80%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E8%88%B9%E6%90%AD%E8%BC%89%E6%8B%96%E7%B6%B2%E3%80%80%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB%E7%A3%81%E5%90%B8%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE</a> <br />\n<br />\n日本發射無人貨運太空船為國際太空站補給物資，以及進行清理太空垃圾的實驗。 <br />\n<br />\n共同社報導，日本宇宙航空研究開發機構（JAXA）昨晚10時26分在鹿兒島縣的種子島宇宙中心，用H2B火箭發射「鸛」號無人貨運太空船。太空船在約15分鐘後進入預定軌道，預計於下周二抵達國際太空站。 <br />\n<br />\n「鸛」號貨運太空船除了補給食物和水外，還搭載7顆超小型衛星、國際太空站的新型電池等，物資總重量約5.9噸。 <br />\n<br />\n「鸛」號貨物太空船轉移物資後，重頭戲是用約一周時間展開清理「宇宙垃圾」實驗。其原理是使用一條垂直的電磁網，把太空垃圾「吸住」，累積到一定重量後下降高度，讓它們進入大氣層時燃燒殆盡。 <br />\n這張拖網是JAXA和漁網生產商日東製網合作研發，花了10年製作，長度為700米。科學家估計要5,000至1萬米長的金屬拖網才能「帶走」太空垃圾。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"609245ddd136413baacd34f93bc99aa132d7c4f4","tid":33954,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:31:26.000Z","msg":"留名等睇lihk仔點睇"},{"pid":"cbc5c9ed8fb7311015fd64670e45b5c54437f241","tid":33954,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"日本仔真係注重環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50ad1549a76e3050ee67e4670cabef4829f8429","tid":33954,"uid":8347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:44:54.000Z","msg":"日本人真係好愛護環境，連太空都會關心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申純日撚</span>"},{"pid":"40041edcab71bf27f756c66d8043dce90753fa01","tid":33954,"uid":39209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"佢唔清咗d 垃圾，點射野上太空呀"},{"pid":"15dfe90b388a17b9c28e951cb7e0ffe51e30b7f6","tid":33954,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"負責任強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔似某國，自稱強，卻貽害全世界"},{"pid":"4546cc342d9874200a9762ea4e9fbf62e6fa6920","tid":33954,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"點分佢係咪垃圾定有用果d"},{"pid":"ff65b83ed2517ed41e579620938cecdea2a33668","tid":33954,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:41:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負責任強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔似某國，自稱強，卻貽害全世界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前射支導彈上去射衛星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e61df6c6f0044ce3b8f52404f57f5eef11a13d","tid